==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: I.Q.
<hw>I.Q.</hw></mhw> <pos>n.</pos> <def>a measure of a
person's intelligence as indicated by an intelligence test; the ratio of
a person's mental age to their chronological age (multiplied by
100).</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> intelligence quotient, IQ.</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source>]</p>

